ns from hell. More details in https://www.htmhell.dev/2-div-with-button-role/ */</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td id=\"file-a11y-dev-mode-css-L35\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number js-blob-rnum\" data-line-number=\"35\"></td>\n          <td id=\"file-a11y-dev-mode-css-LC35\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">div[role=&quot;button&quot;] {</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td id=\"file-a11y-dev-mode-css-L36\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number js-blob-rnum\" data-line-number=\"36\"></td>\n          <td id=\"file-a11y-dev-mode-css-LC36\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">  color: red;</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td id=\"file-a11y-dev-mode-css-L37\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number js-blob-rnum\" data-line-number=\"37\"></td>\n          <td id=\"file-a11y-dev-mode-css-LC37\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">  text-decoration: blink !important;</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td id=\"file-a11y-dev-mode-css-L38\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number js-blob-rnum\" data-line-number=\"38\"></td>\n          <td id=\"file-a11y-dev-mode-css-LC38\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">}</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td id=\"file-a11y-dev-mode-css-L39\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number js-blob-rnum\" data-line-number=\"39\"></td>\n          <td id=\"file-a11y-dev-mode-css-LC39\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">\n</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td id=\"file-a11y-dev-mode-css-L40\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number js-blob-rnum\" data-line-number=\"40\"></td>\n          <td id=\"file-a11y-dev-mode-css-LC40\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">/* highlight on empty anchors/buttons */</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td id=\"file-a11y-dev-mode-css-L41\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number js-blob-rnum\" data-line-number=\"41\"></td>\n          <td id=\"file-a11y-dev-mode-css-LC41\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">button:empty,</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td id=\"file-a11y-dev-mode-css-L42\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number js-blob-rnum\" data-line-number=\"42\"></td>\n          <td id=\"file-a11y-dev-mode-css-LC42\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">a:empty {</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td id=\"file-a11y-dev-mode-css-L43\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number js-blob-rnum\" data-line-number=\"43\"></td>\n          <td id=\"file-a11y-dev-mode-css-LC43\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">  border: 2px dotted red !important;</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td id=\"file-a11y-dev-mode-css-L44\" class=\"blob-num js-line-number js-blob-rnum\" data-line-number=\"44\"></td>\n          <td id=\"file-a11y-dev-mode-css-LC44\" class=\"blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line\">}</td>\n        </tr>\n  </table>\n</div>\n\n\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"gist-meta\">\n        <a href=\"https://gist.github.com/willmendesneto/4302de65ed6fa0e3661d3c0c08cf2a28/raw/cdbfc55d04cc5f0fb5d85257c6ae6f7357071171/a11y-dev-mode.css\" style=\"float:right\" class=\"Link--inTextBlock\">view raw</a>\n        <a href=\"https://gist.github.com/willmendesneto/4302de65ed6fa0e3661d3c0c08cf2a28#file-a11y-dev-mode-css\" class=\"Link--inTextBlock\">\n          a11y-dev-mode.css\n        </a>\n        hosted with &#10084; by <a class=\"Link--inTextBlock\" href=\"https://github.com\">GitHub</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n</div></p>\n<h3>What \"A11Y-Dev-Mode.css\" file is checking?</h3>\n<p>This gist is covering most of the common issues, such as:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>HTML tag <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;html></code> without <code class=\"language-text\">[lang]</code> definition;</li>\n<li>Ordered/Unordered (<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;ol></code> and <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;ul></code>, respectively) HTML lists without a list inside (<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;li></code>) of them;</li>\n<li>Images (<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;img></code>) without <code class=\"language-text\">[alt]</code> attribute;</li>\n<li>Anchor tags (<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;a></code>) without correct <code class=\"language-text\">[href]</code> or even empty;</li>\n<li>Label tags without <code class=\"language-text\">[for]</code> attribute;</li>\n<li>Empty <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;button></code> tags;</li>\n<li>Div tags using <code class=\"language-text\">[role=\"button\"]</code>. It affects some screen readers and browsers, changing the default behaviour of div for people with disabilities;</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>The results</h2>\n<p>As a final result, your page will display elements like this when they're missing some of the mandatory attributes.</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1280px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/eb8691b3f5c01bfa9d8cef6f05c9a6f4/f7d36/a11y-dev-mode-in-action.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 97.1875%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/eb8691b3f5c01bfa9d8cef6f05c9a6f4/fb34c/a11y-dev-mode-in-action.avif 320w,\n/static/eb8691b3f5c01bfa9d8cef6f05c9a6f4/646cd/a11y-dev-mode-in-action.avif 768w,\n/static/eb8691b3f5c01bfa9d8cef6f05c9a6f4/8b485/a11y-dev-mode-in-action.avif 1024w,\n/static/eb8691b3f5c01bfa9d8cef6f05c9a6f4/a73d6/a11y-dev-mode-in-action.avif 1280w,\n/static/eb8691b3f5c01bfa9d8cef6f05c9a6f4/a82e4/a11y-dev-mode-in-action.avif 1836w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"\n              type=\"image/avif\"\n            /><source\n              srcset=\"/static/eb8691b3f5c01bfa9d8cef6f05c9a6f4/cb523/a11y-dev-mode-in-action.webp 320w,\n/static/eb8691b3f5c01bfa9d8cef6f05c9a6f4/cd067/a11y-dev-mode-in-action.webp 768w,\n/static/eb8691b3f5c01bfa9d8cef6f05c9a6f4/53334/a11y-dev-mode-in-action.webp 1024w,\n/static/eb8691b3f5c01bfa9d8cef6f05c9a6f4/4b075/a11y-dev-mode-in-action.webp 1280w,\n/static/eb8691b3f5c01bfa9d8cef6f05c9a6f4/5a428/a11y-dev-mode-in-action.webp 1836w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/eb8691b3f5c01bfa9d8cef6f05c9a6f4/d4f27/a11y-dev-mode-in-action.png 320w,\n/static/eb8691b3f5c01bfa9d8cef6f05c9a6f4/778aa/a11y-dev-mode-in-action.png 768w,\n/static/eb8691b3f5c01bfa9d8cef6f05c9a6f4/658fc/a11y-dev-mode-in-action.png 1024w,\n/static/eb8691b3f5c01bfa9d8cef6f05c9a6f4/26c69/a11y-dev-mode-in-action.png 1280w,\n/static/eb8691b3f5c01bfa9d8cef6f05c9a6f4/f7d36/a11y-dev-mode-in-action.png 1836w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/eb8691b3f5c01bfa9d8cef6f05c9a6f4/26c69/a11y-dev-mode-in-action.png\"\n            alt=\"Final result when using a11y-dev-mode.css file in your app\"\n            title=\"Final result when using a11y-dev-mode.css file in your app\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Final result when using a11y-dev-mode.css file in your app</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>As you can see, this is quite useful and you can import the file only in your local development, improving your dev loop and avoiding these issues to be released to production.</p>\n<p>ü§ò Feel free to play with this example by accessing the <a href=\"https://stackblitz.com/edit/css-skeleton-loader-wai-aria-attributes-twfmhx?file=styles.css\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Stackblitz demo for \"a11y-dev-mode.css\"</a>. ü§ò</p>\n<hr />\n<blockquote>\n<p>‚ö†Ô∏è Please keep in mind this should not be published to production since it's a file used only for debugging purposes. Otherwise you might have issues in your website.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<hr />\n<h3>That‚Äôs all for¬†now</h3>\n<p>This was a quick one, but I hope you enjoyed this reading as much as I enjoyed writing it. Thank you so much for reading until the end and see you soon!</p>\n<hr />\n<h3>Cya üëã</h3>","frontmatter":{"date":"March 17, 2021","path":"/posts/linting-web-accessibility-issues-in-your-html-using-just-css/","title":"Linting Web Accessibility issues in your HTML using just CSS!","tags":["frontend","css","aria","html","tooling","a11y"]},"timeToRead":5}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":["1559850390","63159454"]}